title: PML-N parliamentary delegation from KPK calls on PM Shehbaz
content:
ISLAMABAD, Sep 12 (APP): The parliamentary delegation of the Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz from Khyber Pakhtunkhwa on Thursday called on Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif here.
The delegation comprised Member of National Assembly Sardar Muhammad Yousuf, and members of KPK Assembly Syed Qasim Ali Shah and Sardar Shah Jahan Yousuf.
In the meeting, the parliamentarians apprised the prime minister of the progress in the ongoing development projects in the province.
They also thanked the prime minister for extending federal governmentâ€™s cooperation for timely completion of development projects in KP province.
The parliamentarians lauded the prime minister for his prudent economic policies which brought in the economic stability.
The parliamentary delegation reiterated their cooperation to the government in its initiatives of public welfare.
